--- Astroblast / Dead-End / Drag Strip ---

Dead-End and Drag Strip form their parts of Menasor. Both 
transformed bots, merge with Motormaster's transformed lower 
midsection. When 1the gestalt transformation finishes, Menasor 
rumbles, "Menasor... crush..." (you can have him now Jer =)

Astroblast smiles as Menasor is formed, then he spots the 
incomming Nightstrike. "Nightstrike, patrol the pathway to our 
target location. Have Cyclonus fill you in on the rest of the details."

He spins and yells at the Terrorcons, "Hun-Grr, get you Terrorcons 
in line... wha, where's Blot, he is supposed to be here." (Yan, u 
mind bringing him over? =P)
